{"tid":707302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼二期用地擬引入全洗首個鮮花公園","createTime":"2018-06-18T14:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T15:19:14.000Z","uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9f889cbdc5dab3e7da31f3b061f2ffd7cf7ff9","tid":707302,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"//...政府在大嶼山竹篙灣一直預留60公頃填海土地，供香港迪士尼樂園發展第二期，惟該地已閒置約9年。有公司計劃在該處設花藝文化娛樂主題公園，今日更在荷蘭簽署諒解備忘錄，計劃之後在從荷蘭引入80多種花卉，為香港帶來一片花海，商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華表明，認為計劃可為香港旅遊業增添吸引力。不過公園創辦人表示，仍未正式向政府申請短期租約，公園今年內都未能開放<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華今日亦有到荷蘭，見證簽署合作協議。邱騰華表示，公園為香港引入「花園旅遊概念」，可豐富香港的旅遊體驗，期望除了現有的主題主園、市區、古蹟，花公園可為遊客帶來新選擇...//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/200640/%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%8C%E6%9C%9F%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E5%9C%B0%E8%AE%8A%E8%8A%B1%E6%B5%B7-%E4%B8%BB%E8%BE%A6%E5%95%86-%E6%9C%AA%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A580%E7%A8%AE%E8%8A%B1%E5%8D%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F200640%2F%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%259C%259F%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%258A%25B1%25E6%25B5%25B7-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2595%2586-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B-%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%2585%25A580%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%258D%2589&d=DEPrfqq5BVsZqc%2FvWm%2F6rEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=402c6450\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/200640/%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%8C%E6%9C%9F%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E5%9C%B0%E8%AE%8A%E8%8A%B1%E6%B5%B7-%E4%B8%B